<p>Let's design a <a target="_blank" href="https://whatsapp.com">Whatsapp</a> like instant messaging service, similar to services like <a target="_blank" href="https://www.whatsapp.com">Whatsapp</a>, <a target="_blank" href="https://www.messenger.com">Facebook Messenger</a>, and <a target="_blank" href="https://www.wechat.com">WeChat</a>.</p>
